data.description: Extremely cute house located on Lake Diann. 125ft of private lake shore with a nice sandy shoreline. Large backyard with a very gentle slope to the lake for easy access. Home has been updated from top to bottom. Wake up in the morning and enjoy the beautiful views overlooking the lake. The views are priceless! Pride in homeownership is very evident and with all the updates, you will feel right at home. Perfect lake house to call home or use as a year-round cabin!
